org.ambraproject.rhino.content

Class PersonName

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ambraproject.rhino.content.PersonName

  • public class PersonName
extends Object
    Immutable holder for a name that can be put into ArticlePerson or CitedArticlePerson.

    This is a hack to allow code to write to ArticlePerson and CitedArticlePerson with minimal duplication, because those two classes lack a superclass or interface to unify them.
